Scientific Games Reports First Quarter 2017 Results


Apr. 27, 2017 at 4:05 p.m. ET
on PR Newswire - PRF











Scientific Games Corp.


            
            Scientific Games Corp. engages in the development of technology-based products for the global lottery and regulated gaming industries. It operates its business through the following segments: Gaming, Lottery, and Interactive. The Interactive business segment is comprised solely of their instant products operating segment, which provides instant lottery games; and related value-added services, as well as licensed brands that are printed on instant lottery games and other promotional lottery products. The Lottery segment includes system-based services, and product sales and instant game business particularly instant products-participation and price-per-unit, instant products licensing and player loyalty, and lottery systems services and sales. The Gaming segment designs, develops, manufactures, markets, and distributes gaming products and services; and involves gaming operations, machine sales, systems, and table products. The Interactive segment refers to social gaming through casino-style, slot-based games; real money gaming; and SG Universe play-for-fun and play-for-free white label gaming services. The company was founded on July 2, 1984 and is headquartered in Las Vegas, NV.

            
