Scientific Games Careers


As a technology innovator in the lottery and pari-mutuel industries, Scientific Games Corporation is an exciting place to work. There are a variety of opportunities for people with the right skills ranging from entry-level to top-level professionals in fields like IT, Research and Development, Administrative Support, Finance, and the skilled Technicians and Operators who keep our products operational at our field locations.
Diversity is important to Scientific Games Corporation because our global business appeals to many cultures, nationalities and backgrounds. All of these factors contribute to the success of our organization. 
We believe in a challenging team environment where we constantly strive to excel. Everyone is encouraged to think "outside the box," in order to anticipate our customers’ needs and exceed expectations. 
If you would like more information about joining our team, please reach out to the Talent Acquisition team at SGtalent@scientificgames.com.
Scientific Games acquired WMS and Williams Interactive in 2013 and Bally Technologies in 2014. All job postings from these wholly owned subsidiaries now appear on the Current Openings page.
Scientific Games is an Equal Opportunity Employer dedicated to providing equal opportunity to all employees and applicants regardless of race, color, age, gender, sexual orientation, national origin, marital or veteran status, disability, genetic information,  or any other basis protected by federal, state or local law. The company is committed to providing equal employment opportunity with respect to recruitment, selection and all terms and conditions of employment.






















