Innovation. Technology. Performance.Driving returns for lotteries and beneficiaries worldwide


Research. Results. Revenue.
Our approach to serving your lottery is that simple.
For the last 40 years, we’ve been driving revenue for our lottery customers around the globe. Everything we’ve learned along the way has set the stage for our customers’ success today – and tomorrow.
Scientific Games offers all of the products and technology a lottery needs to perform – from exciting game content, to retail programs, integrated product management, loyalty and rewards programs, interactive platforms, lottery systems, point-of-sale terminals and managed services.
Our trusted solutions are leading the way for lotteries worldwide to maximize returns to beneficiaries and meet their business missions. Because the way we look at it, your success is our success. And it all comes down to results.
The Science Behind Lottery
Every tool Scientific Games offers to help lotteries achieve results is backed by deep marketing research and analysis – and of course, our industry renowned standards for security and integrity. Whether a lottery is established or emerging, we’re here to enable responsible growth – now and in the future.
Scientific Games is a proud member of:World Lottery AssociationEuropean Lotteries AssociationAsia Pacific Lottery AssociationNorth American Association of State and Provincial LotteriesThe Canadian Gaming AssociationLatin American Corporation of State Lottery and BettingAssociation of Gaming Equipment ManufacturersNational Association of Convenience StoresPetroleum Convenience Alliance for Technology StandardsTechnology Association of Georgia






















